meeting-recorder (0.1.2) noble; urgency=medium

  * Fix `meeting-recorder record` never producing a final file: the manual
    record command now waits for the background finalize pass (concat +
    denoise + loudness normalize) instead of exiting immediately, which had
    left orphaned .partN segments and no output .mkv.

 -- Md Salman Siddik <salmansiddik19@gmail.com>  Fri, 17 Jul 2026 21:40:00 +0600

meeting-recorder (0.1.1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Add meeting-recorder start/stop/restart/logs wrappers around
    systemctl --user, so the --user flag is not needed day to day.
  * status now reports the background service state alongside the active
    capture streams and the meeting match.

